SERVER REQUIRMENTS FOR FUSION PRO VERSION3.0

01) SERVER OR VIRTUAL SERVER RUNNING UBUNTUS-SERVER-16.04LTS
02) FULLY PATCHED TO CURRENT.
03) NGINX INSTALLED WITH PHP7.4 AND PHP7.4-FPM LOADED
04) SQL SERVER EXPRESS 2016 WITH REPLICATION OR LATER VERSIONS (IE FULL SQL VERSIONS OK TOO)
05) FUSION SHELL 1.0 INSTALLED FROM GITHUB
06) ADOBE COLDFUSION SERVER 2018 OR LATER INSTALLED AND INTEGRATED WITH THE WEB SERVER
07) MS-SQL COMMAND LINE TOOLS AND PHP PECL INSTALLED
08) MS-ODBC DRIVERS
09) XRDP INSTALLED BY DEFAULT(REMMINA)
10) WEBMIN INSTALLED
11) BIND9 INSTALLED
12) AT LEAST 3.0GB OF RAM FOR THE UBUNTU SERVER AND SQL SERVER
13) THE FOLLOWING DOMAINS PROVISIONED (PEM.DOMAIN.X, GEM.DOMAIN.X, CONFIGURATION.DOMAIN.X, SEM.DOMAIN.X)
14) CERTBOT INSTALLED 
15) GITHUB INSTALLED
16) JOOMLA INSTALLED TO WEBROOT\H
17) WORDPRESS INSTALLED TO WEBROOT\W
18) DRUPAL INSTALLED TO WEBROOT\CMS


15) G/A RECOMMEND THE FOLLOWING GENERAL PURPOSE FILE STRUCTURE FOR OUR COMBINEDTOOLSET SO CREATE THESE DIRECTORIES FIRST:
a) \WEB\GREENVILLE\DOMAIN.XXX      AS WEB ROOT DIRECTORY
b) \WEBLOGS\GREENVILLE\DOMAIN.XXX  AS LOG DIRECTORY
c) \WEBCERTS\GREENVILLE\DOMAIN.XXX AS SSL DIRECTORY
d) \WEB\GREENVILLE\SHAREPOINT2016
e) \WEB\GREENVILLE\SQLSERVER2016
f) \WEB\GREENVILLE\ADOBECOLDFUSION2018
g) \WEB\GREENVILLE\OPENSOURCE\JOOMLA
